estment group. The tool utilizes underlying assumptions based on", "bbox": [153.2, 725.9, 1103.8, 746.7]}, {"text": "actual returns by asset category and inflation and takes into account our asset allocation to derive an expected", "bbox": [153.2, 750.9, 1103.7, 771.7]}, {"text": "long-term rate of return on those assets. Capital market assumptions reflect the long-term capital market outlook.", "bbox": [153.2, 775.9, 1103.7, 796.8]}, {"text": "The assumptions for equity and fixed income investments are developed using a building-block approach,", "bbox": [153.2, 800.9, 1103.7, 821.8]}, {"text": "reflecting observable inflation information and interest rate information available in the fixed income markets.", "bbox": [153.2, 825.9, 1103.6, 846.8]}, {"text": "Long-term assumptions for other asset categories are based on historical results, current market characteristics", "bbox": [153.2, 851.0, 1103.4, 871.8]}, {"text": "and the professional judgment of our internal and external investment teams.", "bbox": [153.2, 876.0, 794.2, 896.8]}, {"text": "Assumed health care cost trend", "bbox": [153.2, 929.1, 422.2, 950.0]}, {"text": "The following summarizes the assumed health care cost trend rates.", "bbox": [153.2, 982.7, 718.1, 1003.5]}, {"text": "December 31,", "bbox": [917.7, 1031.4, 1023.0, 1050.1]}, {"text": "2015", "bbox": [855.7, 1058.5, 893.2, 1077.2]}, {"text": "2014", "bbox": [951.6, 1058.5, 989.1, 1077.2]}, {"text": "2013", "bbox": [1047.5, 1058.5, 1085.0, 1077.2]}, {"text": "Health care cost trend rate assumed for the following year:", "bbox": [153.2, 1098.1, 593.6, 1116.8]}, {"text": "Medical: Pre-65", "bbox": [190.7, 1129.3, 312.2, 1148.1]}, {"text": "7.50%", "bbox": [860.4, 1129.3, 908.9, 1148.1]}, {"text": "8.00%", "bbox": [956.3, 1129.3, 1004.8, 1148.1]}, {"text": "8.00%", "bbox": [1052.2, 1129.3, 1100.6, 1148.1]}, {"text": "Prescription drugs", "bbox": [190.7, 1160.6, 327.8, 1179.4]}, {"text": "7.00%", "bbox": [860.4, 1160.6, 908.9, 1179.4]}, {"text": "7